'''Sector N-Four''' was one of the twelve zones which divided up the northern hemisphere of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|DS-1 Orbital Battle Station]]. It was destroyed along with the rest of the Death Star in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].

